Package org.dei.facts

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Evidence<T,V>
    The Evidence class represents a piece of evidence with a description, fact, and value.
    How
    The How class generates an explanation of how a diagnosis was concluded based on a list of evidences.
    Resposta
    The Resposta class represents a response in the diagnostic tool, containing various details about the selected car, diagnostic results, and related evidences.
    Why
    The Why class represents a collection of evidences and provides a method to obtain the previous question that led to the current suggested question.
